OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FEvery year millions of visitors come
OL,7,Fto Xi'an to visit Emperor Qin's
OL,8,FMausoleum site, ITV News Asia
OL,9,FCorrespondent Debi Edward reports
OL,11,FThe Terracotta Army in Xi'an is
OL,12,Fincredible in its scale, intricacy and
OL,13,Fhistorical significance. We were
OL,14,Finvited to visit on the 50th
OL,15,Fanniversary year of what was one of
OL,16,Fthe most significant archaeological
OL,17,Fdiscoveries of the 20th century.
OL,19,FMore than 8,000 warriors have been
OL,20,Funearthed so far and discoveries are
OL,21,Fstill being made every year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
