OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FAt a special exhibition for the
OL,7,Fanniversary, on display were members
OL,8,Fof what appears to be a full royal
OL,9,Fcourt.
OL,11,FBuried alongside the soldiers and
OL,12,Fhorses, they have found officials,
OL,13,Fmusicians, dancers, terracotta
OL,14,Fstables, and bronze animals.
OL,16,FThe Warriors were built in the third
OL,17,Fcentury BC during the Qin Dynasty to
OL,18,Fsafeguard the tomb of China's first
OL,19,Femperor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
