OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FAccording to ancient beliefs, Emperor
OL,7,FQin thought his power and wealth would
OL,8,Fextend into the afterlife.
OL,10,FAn estimated 700,000 men were enlisted
OL,11,Fto handcraft the life-size army and
OL,12,Fset them in battle formation to
OL,13,Fprotect him in the underworld.
