OL,6,FNew technology has advanced the
OL,7,Fprecision with which archaeologists
OL,8,Fhave been able to piece together this
OL,9,Fmost complex of jigsaw puzzles.
OL,11,FA senior researcher on the restoration
OL,12,Fteam told us that they have
OL,13,Festablished a database, scanning
OL,14,Fimages of the fragments they have
OL,15,Frecovered.
