OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FAssembling the pieces with the help of
OL,7,Fthe computer database has minimised
OL,8,Fthe amount of human intervention
OL,9,Frequired and avoids any unnecessary
OL,10,Fdamage to the relics. They have also
OL,11,Fused 3D imaging to help project how
OL,12,Fsome of the more damaged pieces might
OL,13,Fhave looked.
OL,15,FThey have also been able to recreate
OL,16,Fmore accurately the colours of the
OL,17,FTerracotta Warriors.
OL,19,FMost of them have faded now but it's
OL,20,Fbelieved they were originally all
OL,21,Fbrightly coloured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
