OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FScientists have collected eight
OL,7,Fdifferent kinds of pigments so far,
OL,8,Fmost of them appear to have come from
OL,9,Fmineral or vegetable dye.
OL,11,FThe purple is believed to have been
OL,12,Fmanmade, showing once again how
OL,13,Fadvanced Chinese craftsmanship was
OL,14,Feven in such ancient times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
