OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FOther technology has been deployed to
OL,7,Fhelp with temperature controls both in
OL,8,Fthe museum and while working on the
OL,9,Frestoration of the statues.
OL,10,FControlling the temperature, humidity
OL,11,Fand light exposure can prevent further
OL,12,Fdegradation.
OL,14,FThe Warriors have become an iconic
OL,15,Fsymbol of China's history, showcasing
OL,16,Fthe country's ancient culture and the
OL,17,Fartistry of its people more than 2,000
OL,18,Fyears ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
