OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FEvery year millions of visitors come
OL,7,Fto Xi'an to visit Emperor Qin's
OL,8,FMausoleum site, and in 1986 it was one
OL,9,Fof the first stops made by Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth II and Prince Philip when
OL,11,Fthey made Britain's first royal visit
OL,12,Fto China.
OL,14,FThey were allowed into the largest pit
OL,15,Fto look directly into the faces of the
OL,16,Fwarriors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
