OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FFootage from that visit shows Prince
OL,7,FPhilip walking amongst them with his
OL,8,Fhands in his pockets, and at one point
OL,9,Fcasually picking up a stone and
OL,10,Fturning it over in his hand.
OL,12,FIt turned out to be a piece of
OL,13,Fcharcoal, from an underground fire
OL,14,Fthat had burned many of the materials
OL,15,Fburied with the warriors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
