OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FVisiting on Halloween it did feel like
OL,7,Fat any moment, they could suddenly
OL,8,Fblink and start marching towards us.
OL,10,FIn a workshop near the museum, we went
OL,11,Fto visit Han Pingzhe, who was teaching
OL,12,Fchildren about the moment in 1974 when
OL,13,Ffarmers digging a well found the first
OL,14,Ffragments of the Terracotta Army.
OL,16,FHe was part of the original excavation
OL,17,Fteam and now runs a business making
OL,18,Freplica warriors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
