OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FA group of Malaysian tourists were
OL,7,Fthere making their own souvenir mini-
OL,8,Fwarriors.
OL,10,FPingzhe described what it was like at
OL,11,Fthe very beginning when they were
OL,12,Fpulling the warriors out of the earth,
OL,13,Ftaking them to a restoration site and
OL,14,Fthen seeing them being pieced together
OL,15,Fbit by bit.
OL,17,FIt was painstaking work, and nobody
OL,18,Fhad experienced anything like that
OL,19,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
