OL,3,CThe Terracotta Army showcases the
OL,4,Cartistry of more than 2,000 years ago
OL,6,FHe said it was such a large burial
OL,7,Fsite, full of these huge stone
OL,8,Fsoldiers, nothing of which had been
OL,9,Frecorded in history textbooks and they
OL,10,Fwere full of curiosity to see what the
OL,11,Fwarriors were going to look like, each
OL,12,Fdiffering from the next.
OL,14,FA chance discovery 50 years ago has
OL,15,Fgiven China and the world an
OL,16,Fintriguing insight into one of the
OL,17,Foldest civilisations on earth. And
OL,18,Fthere's still more digging to be done.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
